{"title":"罗马数字","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-3045","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>古罗马人创造了七个记号来表示数字，大家应该都知道。</p>\n<p>I=1，V=5，X=10，L=50，C=100，D=500,M=1000</p>\n<p>计数时按右加左减的法则进行.当数值较小的记号在数值较大的记号的右面的时候，则把两个记号分别代表的数值相加；</p>\n<p>反之，则以较大的数值减去较小的数值，例如：MCXLI表示1141.</p>\n<p>给你一个数字，请你将它转换成罗马数字</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>一个&lt;4000的数字</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>转换成的罗马数字</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1240</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>MCCXL</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>很小，但有点难度</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}